title: Love where you live! 94 walkscore, rooftop views, fitness center 24/7!
posting_body: ['Pricing is all dependent on move-in date and lease length; we offer 3-13-month term options.', 'Our website will show all rates and terms updated each day.', 'Prescott Wallingford', '3920 Stone Way North, Seattle, WA, 98103', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 53', 'OR Text', '53', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'Welcome Home to Prescott Wallingford!', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 545 Sq.', 'Ft.', "Our on-site leasing team is here to help you with all of life's little details including dry cleaning, transportation, dog walking and grocery delivery.", 'Wallingford is a neighborhood close to downtown where you can enjoy all the conveniences city living has to offer.', 'An easy walk to Fremont, Gas Works Park, Fremont Troll and The Sunday Fremont Market; Wallingford is a true cultural destination that all must come an explore.', 'Features', '- Full-Size In-Unit Washer and Dryer', '- Decks, patios, or private rooftop terraces*', '- Vinyl Floors*', '- 17-Foot Ceilings*', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Versatile Track Lighting Systems', '- Vaulted Ceilings*', '- Controlled Access Doors', '- Walk-in Closets*', '*Select units only.', 'Community Amenities', '- Lease Terms from 3-13 months', '- Easy Access to I-5, 99 & Bus Route 62/26', '- Community Lounge w/ Wi-fi', '- Gated Access Parking Garage', '- FOB Access Doors', '- Conference Room w/ Wi-fi', '- Package Lockers', '- Roof -Top w/ Spectacular Views', '- On-Site Storage Units', '- Pea Patch Garden Bins', '- Off-Leash Dog Run', '- On-Site Bike Storage', '- Night Patrol', '- 3 On-Site BBQ Grills', '- Fitness center', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Our apartments accommodate up to two pets per home.', 'Additional deposits and breed restrictions apply.', 'Income Requirements:', 'Income must be 3 times the amount of rent to qualify.', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'pJTEPi4Oht']
